Hi, Bruce--
  Sorry I wasn't more explicit, because your voices deserve lots and lots of oohs and ahhs.  They are, yes, among the best out there.  It's very encouraging (and fascinating) to listen to them, as you seem to really have established real time give-and-take with the other side beyond what most have.
  From a newbie who's impressed by everything: your voices are amazing.
  Ursula
